{"tid":1522535,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「送頭」的意義","createTime":"2019-08-31T13:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T13:49:53.000Z","uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7fc4799d64fca1b4954b46b41cfa7f584f4aa0","tid":1522535,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"有無人答到我咩係人生既意義<br />\n點解人要生存得有尊嚴?<br />\n如果生存可以存在意義<br />\n咁死, 存唔存在意義?<br />\n點樣死, 先係將呢種意義放到最大?<br />\n著黃色雨嬲跳樓?<br />\n<br />\n咁無黃色雨嬲呢?<br />\n6條命入邊, 大家除左黃色雨嬲同女仔, 仲記得邊個?<br />\n<br />\n生存係一種意義, 死係唔係一種意義?<br />\n我相信生存既意義遠比死亡既意義難答<br />\n<br />\n我見連登好多哲學家好鐘意探討事物背後所存在既意義<br />\n小弟係度都想一問各位哲學家,<br />\n生存意義何在, 死亡意義何在?"},{"pid":"c3d50bc057f87aee5c84f7966894129a7d957c54","tid":1522535,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"艾爾文說的，就是就算他們的犧牲對他們自己本身毫無意義，也可以對其他人有意義。就算他們將死去，他們死前所做的事情也可以對活着的人有價值。<br />\n<a href=\"https://corrupttheyouth.net/2019/08/16/%e5%b1%8d%e9%aa%b8%e7%9a%84%e9%81%93%e8%b7%af-%e7%8a%a7%e7%89%b2%e7%9a%84%e6%84%8f%e7%be%a9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorrupttheyouth.net%2F2019%2F08%2F16%2F%25e5%25b1%258d%25e9%25aa%25b8%25e7%259a%2584%25e9%2581%2593%25e8%25b7%25af-%25e7%258a%25a7%25e7%2589%25b2%25e7%259a%2584%25e6%2584%258f%25e7%25be%25a9%2F&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu%2BCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=a9c0674a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://corrupttheyouth.net/2019/08/16/%e5%b1%8d%e9%aa%b8%e7%9a%84%e9%81%93%e8%b7%af-%e7%8a%a7%e7%89%b2%e7%9a%84%e6%84%8f%e7%be%a9/</a>"},{"pid":"1758c72344c7e81c59b8daaab16967c58c172f31","tid":1522535,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T13:47:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=356361801967159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D356361801967159&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu%2BCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=fde239a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=356361801